  <h2>Advisory</h2>

  <p>
    Engagements typically begin after a loss, or when a pending commitment carries material downside.
  </p>

  <p>
    The review defines the decision in writing, lists primary failure paths,
    and identifies who bears the loss in each scenario.
  </p>

  <p>
    See: <a href="/decision-framing">Decision Framing</a> · <a href="/commitment-review">Commitment Review</a>
  </p>

